description: A request to retrieve a page of accessor groups. Accessors will be group by submitter and access requirement.

accessRequirementId.description: The condition to filter by AccessRequirement. Use NULL to ignore this filter.

submitterId.description: The condition to filter by submitter. Use NULL to ignore this filter.

expireBefore.description: The condition to filter by expiration. Use NULL to ignore this filter.

nextPageToken.description: The token to get the next page result. Use NULL to get the first page.
